WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en-GB

00:00:02.060 --> 00:00:03.580
Who will win?

00:00:05.020 --> 00:00:06.100
Come on ATC!

00:00:08.880 --> 00:00:11.420
ATC'65 represents a lot of youth.

00:00:11.680 --> 00:00:14.360
We are a club with 1300 members.

00:00:15.160 --> 00:00:21.440
ATC, the biggest football club in Hengelo where fun comes first.

00:00:21.440 --> 00:00:22.640
Can everyone hear me?

00:00:23.080 --> 00:00:23.660
Yes!

00:00:24.780 --> 00:00:26.940
Then we can start.

00:00:34.240 --> 00:00:36.300
It's so much fun to watch because they do so well...

00:00:36.300 --> 00:00:39.500
the training... and the ladies that organise it.

00:00:39.840 --> 00:00:41.280
I'm very proud.

00:00:48.060 --> 00:00:53.500
The training is mostly based on the games that they play.

00:00:53.600 --> 00:00:56.560
It's about how you handle certain things in games

00:00:56.560 --> 00:00:59.060
and about how you can practise these

00:00:59.060 --> 00:01:01.780
for the actual games.

00:01:02.460 --> 00:01:03.660
Examples of exercises

00:01:04.500 --> 00:01:06.820
Reaction speed

00:01:11.980 --> 00:01:12.760
Fitness

00:01:15.740 --> 00:01:17.160
Posession

00:01:22.800 --> 00:01:23.920
Touch

00:01:29.840 --> 00:01:33.780
I also like the cafetaria and I think the volunteers are really good as well.

00:01:36.760 --> 00:01:38.920
There are a lot of fun activities here.

00:01:38.940 --> 00:01:40.160
It's close to home.

00:01:40.660 --> 00:01:43.460
Even if you don't have a game or training, you can still play football here just for fun.

00:01:43.920 --> 00:01:46.060
It's also just a lot of fun, to play football.

00:02:07.600 --> 00:02:11.320
Victory will come!

